49:13.851 --> 49:16.154
But you had guts.

49:16.187 --> 49:18.156
I got that from you.

49:18.189 --> 49:19.357
(chuckles softly)

49:19.390 --> 49:21.359
Remember that dollhouse?

49:21.392 --> 49:22.994
(chuckles)

49:23.028 --> 49:25.496
How could anyone ever forget?

49:25.530 --> 49:28.033
You asked for it
