50:03.568 --> 50:06.204
I know you didn't
fully understand who I was

50:06.237 --> 50:07.372
or what I went through.

50:07.405 --> 50:09.407
But, that night,

50:09.440 --> 50:11.409
I felt seen by you.

50:13.078 --> 50:16.047
(voice breaking):
And having my daddy...

50:16.081 --> 50:18.716
