50:26.757 --> 50:29.394
I can't let you go.

50:29.427 --> 50:31.729
We're just getting started.

50:31.762 --> 50:34.399
You have to.

50:34.432 --> 50:37.102
It's okay.

50:39.637 --> 50:42.607
I love you, Daddy.

